{"tid":1550831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唱美國國歌，美國人大為感動：應該邀請佢地做美國公民","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T13:21:47.000Z","uid":33307,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba6dff2b42c865f335c4e65dfa4ffbea692ed1c","tid":1550831,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VYWuLoAYrgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVYWuLoAYrgE&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=56679beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VYWuLoAYrgE</a><br />\n<br />\nTop Comments：（我翻譯）<br />\nReck ed：比我地美國人更驕傲，中意！<br />\nJaphet Anciado：睇一次喊一次，佢地用美國國旗作為爭取自由既象徵！神幫幫佢地！<br />\nAdam Noble：堅持信念，自由並非免費<br />\ngxbmb：我們可以帶佢地黎美國？<br />\nTim Young：最好的版本，聽下佢地聲線，完全表達國歌精神<br />\neRMca：應該邀請佢地做公民，智商全球最高，啱晒美國"},{"pid":"69b746d742c112076245c3572097c8bf2106986b","tid":1550831,"uid":160247,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:59:21.000Z","msg":"試下中英都跟住唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流 In angst, tears are shed o&rsquo;er this Land<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨 With rage, fears are crushed, in arms we stand<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透 We rise, undefiled, our voice shall never die<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡 As we yearn, our freedom nighs<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走 With eyes blinded, long it comes the night<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後 In faith, banners high, we pledge to fight<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透 Our flesh, sacrificed, our blood shall write this song<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港 Free this Land, &ldquo;Stand with Hong Kong!&rdquo;<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜 Stars will fall, and darkness fills the air<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲 Storms will break, bedazzled by our gallant flares!<br />\n捍自由 We shall strike<br />\n來齊集這裡 This perilous night<br />\n來全力抗對 Determined to fight<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅&quot; With hope, with song, with dignity!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港 Glory enshrined, break our chains! Hold our lines!<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 Freedom shall rise! Revolution of our Time!<br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽 Liberty thrives, rights divine, in our unending strides<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港 Glory be to thee, Hong Kong!"},{"pid":"7e2e1778a457ba207c655f01f465a1658a056e87","tid":1550831,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79a3ba31f88b0d6de832240bf3b9bf754a28f151","tid":1550831,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc72db4512d9467268a182849dad2facff31c14c","tid":1550831,"uid":2757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"彭斯真名上連登冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063b9531537b06b3e398cb2c42d292052c5825a8","tid":1550831,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc72db4512d9467268a182849dad2facff31c14c","tid":1550831,"uid":2757,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"彭斯真名上連登冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg